{"id":618133,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/09/【麻辣总局】郭沫若大跃进诗歌看来也没过时/","date":"2019-09-23T08:13:44Z","modified":"2019-09-24T07:09:48Z","title":"【麻辣总局】“郭沫若大跃进诗歌看来也没过时”","content":"<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EFEot4cUwAAsu4k.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-618134\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EFEot4cUwAAsu4k.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"266\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EFEot4cVUAAHPST.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-618135\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EFEot4cVUAAHPST.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"173\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EFEot4cVUAAHPST.jpeg 320w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EFEot4cVUAAHPST-300x129.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>十一临近，不少网民转发一首据称是“马屁诗人”郭沫若曾经创作的《何人唱红歌》，来讽刺中国正在进行的轰轰烈烈的庆祝活动：</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote><p>三江四海迎盛世，</p>\n<p>五禽六畜喜心窝。</p>\n<p>鸡鸭结伴跳红舞，</p>\n<p>猪狗比赛唱红歌。</p></blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>推特用户 @Frankz_2017 指出：</p>\n<p>这是一位名叫比目鱼的网友2011年的恶搞之作。他还仿冒了胡兰成，康生，孙中山，徐志摩，鲁迅等人的文字和书法。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://dongyangjing.com/bbs_disp.cgi?zno=80403&amp;&amp;kno=001&amp;&amp;no=2207&amp;&amp;hfno=0001&amp;&amp;tit=%BB%D8%B8%B4%5B1%5D%C2%A5\">http://dongyangjing.com/bbs_disp.cgi?zno=80403&amp;&amp;kno=001&amp;&amp;no=2207&amp;&amp;hfno=0001&amp;&amp;tit=%BB%D8%B8%B4%5B1%5D%C2%A5</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>最原始的出处</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bimuyu.com/blog/archives/142992622.shtml\">https://bimuyu.com/blog/archives/142992622.shtml</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>比目鱼仿造的一幅孙中山的题字内容为：</p>\n<blockquote><p>革命尚未成功，屌丝仍须努力。</p></blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>CDS档案 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%9B%BD%E5%BA%86\">国庆</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-618170 size-thumbnail\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/共青团中央-活动-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/共青团中央-活动-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/共青团中央-活动-674x675.jpg 674w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/共青团中央-活动-440x440.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/共青团中央-活动-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></strong></p></blockquote>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,10466,13789],"tags":[8740,11818,33450,14966]}